3) $\bar{q}\left\{x z,-y z^{2}, x y\right\}$ along the closed line (L) $z=x^{2}-y^{2}+2 a^{2}$, $x^{2}+y^{2}=a^{2}$ (see fig. 142, p. 258) and the vorticity vector of this field at the point $A\left(0,-a, a^{2}\right)$.

original.solution:
## Solution

$$
