& =\frac{1}{1+\frac{(2 x+1)^{2}}{2}}+\frac{2\left(4 x^{2}+4 x+3\right)-(2 x+1)(8 x+4)}{\left(4 x^{2}+4 x+3\right)^{2}}=\frac{2}{4 x^{2}+4 x+3}+\frac{8 x^{2}+8 x+6-16 x^{2}-8 x-8 x-4}{\left(4 x^{2}+4 x+3\right)^{2}}= \\
& =\frac{2\left(4 x^{2}+4 x+3\right)-8 x^{2}-8 x+2}{\left(4 x^{2}+4 x+3\right)^{2}}=\frac{8}{\left(4 x^{2}+4 x+3\right)^{2}}
\end{aligned}
$$

## Problem Kuznetsov Differentiation 13-27

