& =\frac{\sqrt[5]{\operatorname{ctg} 2}}{36} \cdot\left(\frac{\cos ^{2} 18 x}{2 \sin 18 x \cdot \cos 18 x}\right)^{\prime}=\frac{\sqrt[5]{\operatorname{ctg} 2}}{72} \cdot\left(\frac{\cos 18 x}{\sin 18 x}\right)^{\prime}= \\
& =\frac{\sqrt[5]{\operatorname{ctg} 2}}{72} \cdot(\operatorname{ctg} 18 x)^{\prime}=\frac{\sqrt[5]{\operatorname{ctg} 2}}{72} \cdot \frac{-1}{\sin ^{2} 18 x} \cdot 18=-\frac{\sqrt[5]{\operatorname{ctg} 2}}{4 \sin ^{2} 18 x}
