& =\sin (\cos 3) \cdot\left(\frac{\cos 2 x}{8 \sin 2 x}\right)^{\prime}=\frac{\sin (\cos 3)}{8} \cdot(\operatorname{ctg} 2 x)^{\prime}= \\
