& =\frac{1}{\sqrt{a^{2}+b^{2}}} \cdot \frac{b}{\sqrt{b^{2}-\left(a^{2}+b^{2}\right) \cdot \sin ^{2} x}} \cdot \frac{\sqrt{a^{2}+b^{2}}}{b} \cdot \cos x= \\
& =\frac{\cos x}{\sqrt{b^{2} \cdot\left(1-\sin ^{2} x\right)-a^{2} \cdot \sin ^{2} x}}=\frac{\cos x}{\sqrt{b^{2} \cdot \cos ^{2} x-a^{2} \cdot \sin ^{2} x}}
